{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0001", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 1, "text_original": "子墨子言曰：", "text_normalized": "子墨子言曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.1", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0002", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 2, "text_original": "天下之王公大人，皆欲其國家之富也，人民之衆也，刑法之治也。", "text_normalized": "天下之王公大人，皆欲其國家之富也，人民之衆也，刑法之治也。", "canonical_ref": "10.2", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0003", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 3, "text_original": "然而不識以尚賢爲政其國家百姓，王公大人本失尚賢爲政之本也。", "text_normalized": "然而不識以尚賢爲政其國家百姓，王公大人本失尚賢爲政之本也。", "canonical_ref": "10.3", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0004", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 4, "text_original": "苟若王公大人本失尚賢爲政之本也，則不能毋舉物示之乎？", "text_normalized": "苟若王公大人本失尚賢爲政之本也，則不能毋舉物示之乎？", "canonical_ref": "10.4", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0005", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 5, "text_original": "今若有一諸侯於此，爲政其國家也，曰：", "text_normalized": "今若有一諸侯於此，爲政其國家也，曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.5", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0006", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 6, "text_original": "「凡我國能射御之士，我將賞貴之。", "text_normalized": "「凡我國能射御之士，我將賞貴之。", "canonical_ref": "10.6", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0007", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 7, "text_original": "不能射御之士，我將罪賤之。", "text_normalized": "不能射御之士，我將罪賤之。", "canonical_ref": "10.7", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0008", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 8, "text_original": "」問於若國之士，孰喜孰懼？", "text_normalized": "」問於若國之士，孰喜孰懼？", "canonical_ref": "10.8", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0009", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 9, "text_original": "我以爲必能射御之士喜，不能射御之士懼。", "text_normalized": "我以爲必能射御之士喜，不能射御之士懼。", "canonical_ref": "10.9", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0010", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 10, "text_original": "我賞因而誘之矣，曰：", "text_normalized": "我賞因而誘之矣，曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.10", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0011", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 11, "text_original": "「凡我國之忠信之士，我將賞貴之。", "text_normalized": "「凡我國之忠信之士，我將賞貴之。", "canonical_ref": "10.11", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0012", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 12, "text_original": "不忠信之士，我將罪賤之。", "text_normalized": "不忠信之士，我將罪賤之。", "canonical_ref": "10.12", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0013", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 13, "text_original": "」問於若國之士，孰喜孰懼？", "text_normalized": "」問於若國之士，孰喜孰懼？", "canonical_ref": "10.13", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0014", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 14, "text_original": "我以爲必忠信之士喜，不忠不信之士懼。", "text_normalized": "我以爲必忠信之士喜，不忠不信之士懼。", "canonical_ref": "10.14", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0015", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 15, "text_original": "今惟毋以尚賢爲政其國家百姓，使國爲善者勸，爲暴者沮。", "text_normalized": "今惟毋以尚賢爲政其國家百姓，使國爲善者勸，爲暴者沮。", "canonical_ref": "10.15", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0016", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 16, "text_original": "大以爲政於天下，使天下之爲善者勸，爲暴者沮。", "text_normalized": "大以爲政於天下，使天下之爲善者勸，爲暴者沮。", "canonical_ref": "10.16", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0017", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 17, "text_original": "然昔吾所以貴堯、舜、禹、湯、文、武之道者，何故以哉？", "text_normalized": "然昔吾所以貴堯、舜、禹、湯、文、武之道者，何故以哉？", "canonical_ref": "10.17", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0018", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 18, "text_original": "以其唯毋臨衆發政而治民，使天下之爲善者可而勸也，爲暴者可而沮也。", "text_normalized": "以其唯毋臨衆發政而治民，使天下之爲善者可而勸也，爲暴者可而沮也。", "canonical_ref": "10.18", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0019", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 19, "text_original": "然則此尚賢者也，與堯、舜、禹、湯、文、武之道同矣。", "text_normalized": "然則此尚賢者也，與堯、舜、禹、湯、文、武之道同矣。", "canonical_ref": "10.19", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0020", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 20, "text_original": "而今天下之士君子，居處言語皆尚賢，逮至其臨衆發政而治民，莫知尚賢而使能。", "text_normalized": "而今天下之士君子，居處言語皆尚賢，逮至其臨衆發政而治民，莫知尚賢而使能。", "canonical_ref": "10.20", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0021", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 21, "text_original": "我以此知天下之士君子，明於小，而不明於大也。", "text_normalized": "我以此知天下之士君子，明於小，而不明於大也。", "canonical_ref": "10.21", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0022", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 22, "text_original": "何以知其然乎？", "text_normalized": "何以知其然乎？", "canonical_ref": "10.22", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0023", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 23, "text_original": "今王公大人有一牛羊之財，不能殺，必索良宰。", "text_normalized": "今王公大人有一牛羊之財，不能殺，必索良宰。", "canonical_ref": "10.23", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0024", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 24, "text_original": "有一衣裳之財，不能制，必索良工。", "text_normalized": "有一衣裳之財，不能制，必索良工。", "canonical_ref": "10.24", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0025", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 25, "text_original": "當王公大人之於此也，雖有骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，實知其不能也，不使之也。", "text_normalized": "當王公大人之於此也，雖有骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，實知其不能也，不使之也。", "canonical_ref": "10.25", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0026", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 26, "text_original": "是何故？", "text_normalized": "是何故？", "canonical_ref": "10.26", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0027", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 27, "text_original": "恐其敗財也。", "text_normalized": "恐其敗財也。", "canonical_ref": "10.27", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0028", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 28, "text_original": "當王公大人之於此也，則不失尚賢而使能。", "text_normalized": "當王公大人之於此也，則不失尚賢而使能。", "canonical_ref": "10.28", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0029", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 29, "text_original": "王公大人有一罷馬不能治，必索良醫。", "text_normalized": "王公大人有一罷馬不能治，必索良醫。", "canonical_ref": "10.29", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0030", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 30, "text_original": "有一危弓不能張，必索良工。", "text_normalized": "有一危弓不能張，必索良工。", "canonical_ref": "10.30", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0031", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 31, "text_original": "當王公大人之於此也，雖有骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，實知其不能也，必不使。", "text_normalized": "當王公大人之於此也，雖有骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，實知其不能也，必不使。", "canonical_ref": "10.31", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0032", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 32, "text_original": "是何故？", "text_normalized": "是何故？", "canonical_ref": "10.32", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0033", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 33, "text_original": "恐其敗財也。", "text_normalized": "恐其敗財也。", "canonical_ref": "10.33", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0034", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 34, "text_original": "當王公大人之於此也，則不失尚賢而使能。", "text_normalized": "當王公大人之於此也，則不失尚賢而使能。", "canonical_ref": "10.34", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0035", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 35, "text_original": "逮至其國家則不然，王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，則舉之。", "text_normalized": "逮至其國家則不然，王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，則舉之。", "canonical_ref": "10.35", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0036", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 36, "text_original": "則王公大人之親其國家也，不若親其一危弓、罷馬、衣裳、牛羊之財與！", "text_normalized": "則王公大人之親其國家也，不若親其一危弓、罷馬、衣裳、牛羊之財與！", "canonical_ref": "10.36", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0037", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 37, "text_original": "我以此知天下之士君子，皆明於小，而不明於大也。", "text_normalized": "我以此知天下之士君子，皆明於小，而不明於大也。", "canonical_ref": "10.37", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0038", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 38, "text_original": "此譬猶瘖者而使爲行人，聾者而使爲樂師。", "text_normalized": "此譬猶瘖者而使爲行人，聾者而使爲樂師。", "canonical_ref": "10.38", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0039", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 39, "text_original": "是故古之聖王之治天下也，其所富，其所貴，未必王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者也。", "text_normalized": "是故古之聖王之治天下也，其所富，其所貴，未必王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者也。", "canonical_ref": "10.39", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0040", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 40, "text_original": "是故昔者，舜耕於歷山，陶於河瀕，漁於雷澤，灰於常陽，堯得之服澤之陽，立爲天子，使接天下之政，而治天下之民。", "text_normalized": "是故昔者，舜耕於歷山，陶於河瀕，漁於雷澤，灰於常陽，堯得之服澤之陽，立爲天子，使接天下之政，而治天下之民。", "canonical_ref": "10.40", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0041", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 41, "text_original": "昔伊尹爲莘氏女師僕，使爲庖人，湯得而舉之，立爲三公，使接天下之政，治天下之民。", "text_normalized": "昔伊尹爲莘氏女師僕，使爲庖人，湯得而舉之，立爲三公，使接天下之政，治天下之民。", "canonical_ref": "10.41", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0042", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 42, "text_original": "昔者傅說居北海之洲，圜土之上，衣褐帶索，庸築於傅巖之城，武丁得而舉之，立爲三公，使之接天下之政，而治天下之民。", "text_normalized": "昔者傅說居北海之洲，圜土之上，衣褐帶索，庸築於傅巖之城，武丁得而舉之，立爲三公，使之接天下之政，而治天下之民。", "canonical_ref": "10.42", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0043", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 43, "text_original": "是故昔者堯之舉舜也，湯之舉伊尹也，武丁之舉傅說也，豈以爲骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者哉？", "text_normalized": "是故昔者堯之舉舜也，湯之舉伊尹也，武丁之舉傅說也，豈以爲骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者哉？", "canonical_ref": "10.43", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0044", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 44, "text_original": "惟法其言，用其謀，行其道，上可而利天，中可而利鬼，下可而利人，是故推而上之。", "text_normalized": "惟法其言，用其謀，行其道，上可而利天，中可而利鬼，下可而利人，是故推而上之。", "canonical_ref": "10.44", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0045", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 45, "text_original": "古者聖王旣審尚賢，欲以爲政，故書之竹帛，琢之槃盂，傳以遺後世子孫。", "text_normalized": "古者聖王旣審尚賢，欲以爲政，故書之竹帛，琢之槃盂，傳以遺後世子孫。", "canonical_ref": "10.45", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0046", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 46, "text_original": "於先王之書《呂刑》之書然：", "text_normalized": "於先王之書《呂刑》之書然：", "canonical_ref": "10.46", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0047", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 47, "text_original": "「王曰：", "text_normalized": "「王曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.47", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0048", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 48, "text_original": "於！", "text_normalized": "於！", "canonical_ref": "10.48", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0049", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 49, "text_original": "來！", "text_normalized": "來！", "canonical_ref": "10.49", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0050", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 50, "text_original": "有國有土，告女訟刑。", "text_normalized": "有國有土，告女訟刑。", "canonical_ref": "10.50", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0051", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 51, "text_original": "在今而安百姓，女何擇言人？", "text_normalized": "在今而安百姓，女何擇言人？", "canonical_ref": "10.51", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0052", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 52, "text_original": "何敬不刑？", "text_normalized": "何敬不刑？", "canonical_ref": "10.52", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0053", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 53, "text_original": "何度不及？", "text_normalized": "何度不及？", "canonical_ref": "10.53", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0054", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 54, "text_original": "」能擇人而敬爲刑，堯、舜、禹、湯、文、武之道可及也。", "text_normalized": "」能擇人而敬爲刑，堯、舜、禹、湯、文、武之道可及也。", "canonical_ref": "10.54", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0055", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 55, "text_original": "是何也？", "text_normalized": "是何也？", "canonical_ref": "10.55", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0056", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 56, "text_original": "則以尚賢及之。", "text_normalized": "則以尚賢及之。", "canonical_ref": "10.56", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0057", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 57, "text_original": "於先王之書《豎年》之言然，曰：", "text_normalized": "於先王之書《豎年》之言然，曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.57", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0058", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 58, "text_original": "「唏夫聖武知人，以屏輔而身。", "text_normalized": "「唏夫聖武知人，以屏輔而身。", "canonical_ref": "10.58", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0059", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 59, "text_original": "」此言先王之治天下也，必選擇賢者，以爲其群屬輔佐。", "text_normalized": "」此言先王之治天下也，必選擇賢者，以爲其群屬輔佐。", "canonical_ref": "10.59", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0060", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 60, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.60", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0061", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 61, "text_original": "今也天下之士君子，皆欲富貴而惡貧賤。", "text_normalized": "今也天下之士君子，皆欲富貴而惡貧賤。", "canonical_ref": "10.61", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0062", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 62, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.62", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0063", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 63, "text_original": "然。", "text_normalized": "然。", "canonical_ref": "10.63", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0064", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 64, "text_original": "女何爲而得富貴而辟貧賤？", "text_normalized": "女何爲而得富貴而辟貧賤？", "canonical_ref": "10.64", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0065", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 65, "text_original": "莫若爲賢。", "text_normalized": "莫若爲賢。", "canonical_ref": "10.65", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0066", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 66, "text_original": "爲賢之道將奈何？", "text_normalized": "爲賢之道將奈何？", "canonical_ref": "10.66", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0067", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 67, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.67", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0068", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 68, "text_original": "有力者疾以助人，有財者勉以分人，有道者勸以教人。", "text_normalized": "有力者疾以助人，有財者勉以分人，有道者勸以教人。", "canonical_ref": "10.68", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0069", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 69, "text_original": "若此，則飢者得食，寒者得衣，亂者得治。", "text_normalized": "若此，則飢者得食，寒者得衣，亂者得治。", "canonical_ref": "10.69", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0070", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 70, "text_original": "若飢則得食，寒則得衣，亂則得治，此安生生。", "text_normalized": "若飢則得食，寒則得衣，亂則得治，此安生生。", "canonical_ref": "10.70", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0071", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 71, "text_original": "今王公大人，其所富，其所貴，皆王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者也。", "text_normalized": "今王公大人，其所富，其所貴，皆王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者也。", "canonical_ref": "10.71", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0072", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 72, "text_original": "今王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，焉故必知哉？", "text_normalized": "今王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，焉故必知哉？", "canonical_ref": "10.72", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0073", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 73, "text_original": "若不知，使治其國家，則其國家之亂可得而知也。", "text_normalized": "若不知，使治其國家，則其國家之亂可得而知也。", "canonical_ref": "10.73", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0074", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 74, "text_original": "今天下之士君子，皆欲富貴而惡貧賤。", "text_normalized": "今天下之士君子，皆欲富貴而惡貧賤。", "canonical_ref": "10.74", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0075", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 75, "text_original": "然女何爲而得富貴而辟貧賤哉？", "text_normalized": "然女何爲而得富貴而辟貧賤哉？", "canonical_ref": "10.75", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0076", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 76, "text_original": "曰：", "text_normalized": "曰：", "canonical_ref": "10.76", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0077", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 77, "text_original": "莫若爲王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者。", "text_normalized": "莫若爲王公大人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者。", "canonical_ref": "10.77", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0078", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 78, "text_original": "王公人人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，此非可學能者也。", "text_normalized": "王公人人骨肉之親、無故富貴、面目美好者，此非可學能者也。", "canonical_ref": "10.78", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0079", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 79, "text_original": "使不知辯，德行之厚，若禹、湯、文、武，不加得也。", "text_normalized": "使不知辯，德行之厚，若禹、湯、文、武，不加得也。", "canonical_ref": "10.79", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0080", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 80, "text_original": "王公大人骨肉之親，躄、瘖、聾，暴爲桀紂，不加失也。", "text_normalized": "王公大人骨肉之親，躄、瘖、聾，暴爲桀紂，不加失也。", "canonical_ref": "10.80", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0081", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 81, "text_original": "是故以賞不當賢，罰不當暴。", "text_normalized": "是故以賞不當賢，罰不當暴。", "canonical_ref": "10.81", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0082", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 82, "text_original": "其所賞者，已無故矣。", "text_normalized": "其所賞者，已無故矣。", "canonical_ref": "10.82", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0083", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 83, "text_original": "其所罰者，亦無罪。", "text_normalized": "其所罰者，亦無罪。", "canonical_ref": "10.83", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0084", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 84, "text_original": "是以使百姓皆攸心解體，沮以爲善。", "text_normalized": "是以使百姓皆攸心解體，沮以爲善。", "canonical_ref": "10.84", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0085", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 85, "text_original": "垂其股肱之力而不相勞來也，腐臭餘財而不相分資也，隱慝良道而不相教誨也。", "text_normalized": "垂其股肱之力而不相勞來也，腐臭餘財而不相分資也，隱慝良道而不相教誨也。", "canonical_ref": "10.85", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0086", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 86, "text_original": "若此，則飢者不得食，寒者不得衣，亂者不得治。", "text_normalized": "若此，則飢者不得食，寒者不得衣，亂者不得治。", "canonical_ref": "10.86", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0087", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 87, "text_original": "推而上之以。", "text_normalized": "推而上之以。", "canonical_ref": "10.87", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0088", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 88, "text_original": "是故昔者，堯有舜，舜有禹，禹有皋陶，湯有小臣，武王有閎夭、泰顚、南宮括、散宜生，而天下和，庶民阜。", "text_normalized": "是故昔者，堯有舜，舜有禹，禹有皋陶，湯有小臣，武王有閎夭、泰顚、南宮括、散宜生，而天下和，庶民阜。", "canonical_ref": "10.88", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0089", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 89, "text_original": "是以近者安之，遠者歸之。", "text_normalized": "是以近者安之，遠者歸之。", "canonical_ref": "10.89", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0090", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 90, "text_original": "日月之所照，舟車之所及，雨露之所漸，粒食之所養，得此莫不勸譽。", "text_normalized": "日月之所照，舟車之所及，雨露之所漸，粒食之所養，得此莫不勸譽。", "canonical_ref": "10.90", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0091", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 91, "text_original": "且今天下之王公大人士君子，中實將欲爲仁義，求爲上士，上欲中聖王之道，下欲中國家百姓之利。", "text_normalized": "且今天下之王公大人士君子，中實將欲爲仁義，求爲上士，上欲中聖王之道，下欲中國家百姓之利。", "canonical_ref": "10.91", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0092", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 92, "text_original": "故尚賢之爲說，而不可不察此者也。", "text_normalized": "故尚賢之爲說，而不可不察此者也。", "canonical_ref": "10.92", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3__seg-0093", "section_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii", "source_id": "mozi-010-exaltation-of-the-virtuous-iii__chinesenotes-1f6b1d3", "work_id": "mozi", "segment_type": "sentence", "segment_order": 93, "text_original": "尚賢者，天鬼百姓之利，而政事之本也。", "text_normalized": "尚賢者，天鬼百姓之利，而政事之本也。", "canonical_ref": "10.93", "notes": ""}
